issues.description: The return type of getStockIngredients() in Stock differs between the template and solution. In the template, it returns a List<StockIngredient>, while in the solution it returns StockIngredient[]. This inconsistency could confuse students comparing the provided template with the reference implementation.
issues.suggested_fix: Align the signature of getStockIngredients() in both template and solution. Either change the solution to return List<StockIngredient> (as in the template) or update the template to return StockIngredient[] to match the solution.
